      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KISAUNI (1) rocketed out of the boxes with a strong early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (30.58) at this track over 530m. Goes very well from this draw with six wins and three minor placings from 10 starts. Good form should continue. MALLEE BEAUTY (7) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (30.24) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including 26 wins. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Expected to be in this for a long way. MANIFESTO (3) is an honest type rarely out of the money, scoring at Gawler (30.57) last time and making it two straight wins. Form at this distance is sound. Best form too dangerous to ignore. Have to include. REALITY IS (5) missed when well in commission last time but a better run is on the cards.",
